name: java-scanner-access-twain
description: Asprise Scanning and Imageing SDK offers a high performance API library so that you can acquire images from and have total control on almost all kinds of scanners on both Windows 32bit and 64bit. Further more, you can rest assured that the SDK is fully compliant with various government privacy acts such as HIPPA and HITECH. High speed ADF scanning allows the end user to scan multiple pages into a ultra small size multi-page TIFF or PDF file. New customers should select this SDK instead of JTwain for compatibility and future proof.
